by the authority of the nation.

31
00:01:16,777 --> 00:01:18,679
Concerning every deleted voice mail,

32
00:01:18,779 --> 00:01:20,781
there won't be enough cops
to deploy!"

33
00:01:20,881 --> 00:01:22,883
Yes, but texts are different.

34
00:01:22,983 --> 00:01:24,485
